- `TELEGRAM_TOKEN`, `TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL`
- `SUPABASE_URL`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`
- `GEMINI_API_KEY`
- `QSTASH_URL`, `QSTASH_TOKEN`
